description: Beautiful corner penthouse with a private deck, water views and 1 full parking space ideally located directly across from Carson Beach. This 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom floor through features a desirable open kitchen with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops and gas cooking. The sun splashed, spacious living room offers ocean views with a gas fireplace in addition to a separate area perfect for either dining and/or a home office. Additional features include central AC, in unit washer/dryer and extra private storage. This offering is complete with a private outdoor deck & 1 full parking space. Building is pet friendly with elevator access. Just steps to the beach, a dog park and everything Southie has to offer. This home truly has it all.
